{"tid":1624711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想同昨晚（10月4號）出左大埔既手足講幾句","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:29:54.000Z","uid":247905,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1c0ff93bdbd89613e5dcaf1e23539e32de914d6b","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:39:27.000Z","msg":"讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：首先係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">從來未見過大埔咁多人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而可能大家都有共識留返係自己區玩，見到好多勇武都留守返大埔做野，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而每當有行動，極大量手足衝上前開傘cover！</span></span><br />\n依點真係極大進步，以往大埔一直俾人笑和理非基地，死攬連儂隧道唱歌嘻哈，依家相信不少和班非都進化左，就算唔參與激進行為，都可以盡量配合勇武做野<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：探完大元民建聯果陣，街市果邊突然叫人跑走，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後面既人未睇清楚咩事就向哂後跑走，而事實係一隻狗都無</span></span><br />\n我明白大多數人都會好驚，但係其實中後排真係可以睇清楚發生咩事先，難聽D講句有事都未到你果邊有事，你真係咁驚都可以跑幾步望返轉頭睇下做咩嘛，果陣有個手足叫到聲都沙埋話：「咩事都唔知就走，咁點反抗呀？」我相當認同<br />\n歡迎各位大埔手足補充/討論<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">黎緊如果大家有共識十八區起義，我地大埔友真係要一齊進步好無？你地都唔想D勇武灰心出哂去玩架嘛？<br />\n就算大埔做唔到黃大仙/元朗果D級數，起碼都唔好落後咁多丫，大埔人一齊進化吧！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>光復香港，時代革命<br />\n香港人，<del>加油</del> 反抗！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（網上轉載，本人支持警察嚴正執法，支持林鄭永續特首）"},{"pid":"3ab5a129ca9b26f76869aecd21eae087dd1a0d10","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d812dec6c0efd19c565c4483b518619af360b4bd","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9fd1cada572d50d609eda9024bc0926a2cdb55","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de2116b07ed372f64f305f533c3d15888672c6d","tid":1624711,"uid":297634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"大埔人琴晚好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5230dd9005d866810175c70957e8a199063dd73e","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0de2116b07ed372f64f305f533c3d15888672c6d","tid":1624711,"uid":297634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"大埔人琴晚好叻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:47:40.000Z","msg":"有進步，但仍有改善空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a72c459d511132a787b73a7dc404e58a364d9a","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c901e2a54ace887f97bcd61acd71827f590c95e0","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a4ff42739745357a4e7dfba4bbda0269f451dd3","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a4af6f0c70c3e6c806bbe5474cdc136cc3916b","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T05:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96a137055a3ef1fd19f1932c4afbfda6a87a646","tid":1624711,"uid":247905,"like":0,"dislike"